        <updateDate>2021-09-24T16:20:34Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Firearm Due Process Protection Act</b></p> <p>This bill revises the hearing procedure and remedy for an individual who (1) was denied a firearm due to erroneous information provided by a state or the National Instant Criminal Background Check System concerning the individual, or (2) was denied a firearm but was not prohibited from receiving a firearm. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
